    "notes": "Wan 2.2 T2V-A14B via Diffusers GPU service. MoE architecture: 27B total params (2x 14B experts, 14B active per step). With FP8 quantization: ~14GB VRAM. BF16: ~40GB VRAM. VAE runs in float32.",
